The use of XGBoost algorithm for learning also suggests that the paper may belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) or cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-categories, which often use this algorithm. Finally, the paper also discusses the ATP/ML feedback loop, which suggests that it may belong to the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category.
